    <div class="main review-item" id="1469317">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1469317/" class="title-link">希望再次重印，价格适中</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1469317"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2808982/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2808982/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">min</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-08-13"
      class="main-meta">2008-08-13 15:42:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1469317_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1990年代，参加北京三联书店的读者俱乐部，他们寄来的购书目录中，就有《泰晤士世界历史地图集》，定价250元，可惜当时没有购买，很是遗憾。上海的公共图书馆中也很少看到。希望三联书店能够再次重印，价格适中。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1469317/#comments">(17回应)</a>
